PRIVACY NOTICE

This software stores all data locally in your browser using IndexedDB.

- No data is sent to external servers (except carrier APIs)
- API keys are stored in browser localStorage
- Users control their own data
- No analytics or tracking implemented
- Optional cloud sync (Firebase/Supabase) requires user opt-in

Users are responsible for:
- Protecting their own API keys
- Understanding carrier data policies
- Managing their own stored shipment data
- Ensuring compliance with applicable privacy laws (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)

================================================================================

DATA USAGE AND RETENTION

This software is designed for personal and business use to track shipments.

PERMITTED USES:
- Personal shipment tracking
- Business logistics management
- Internal company tracking dashboards
- Educational purposes
- Development and testing

PROHIBITED USES:
- Commercial resale of carrier data without authorization
- Competitive intelligence gathering
- Automated scraping at scale
- Violation of carrier API rate limits
- Sharing API keys across multiple users/organizations
- Using data for purposes outside carrier API terms

DATA RETENTION:
- Users control retention periods for stored tracking data
- Raw API payloads can be pruned manually or automatically
- No automated data deletion (user discretion)
- Export functionality allows data portability

